}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The device is manufactured by Senao. The device appears to be identical to the [[EnGenius EIR900]].
"7016A049100a V-1.00" appears to be silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :There appears to be an '''IDT''' PCI-Express switch on the board (89HPES5T5?). :A2HP02 is printed on the label of one of the wireless modules. All of the antennas used are '''Airgain''' antennas (3x N2420DS, 3x N5x20SC).
The power adapter included with the unit is a '''Powertron Electronics''' PA1045-120HUB (100-240VAC ~ 50/60 Hz, 1.0A -> 12VDC, 3.3A).
